\end_layout

\end_inset

 is isostructural to the Zn(II) loaded protein.
 However one cannot rule out the possibility that the affinity of the Hg(II)
 is not detrimental for the functioning of the 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
gls{mrn}
\end_layout

\end_inset

